text: Park Jung-min and Park Jeong-min is a Korean name consisting of the family name Park and the given name Jung-min, and may also refer to: *Park Jung-min (actor) (born 1987), South Korean actor *Park Jung-min (singer) (born 1987), South Korean singer and a member of SS501 *Park Jeong-min (footballer) (born 1988), South Korean footballer
title: Park Jung-min
